  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, the investigators will be developing and testing a mobile phone text message
      intervention to reduce alcohol use for people at risk of alcohol dependence. The
      investigators hypothesize that this intervention will be acceptable to participants, and that
      they will stay in the intervention until it's one week completion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
